'''Caroline de Souza Correa''' (born [[May 19]], [[1979]]) is a [[Wikipedia:Brazilian people|Brazilian]] actress and model who portrayed [[Sheltay Retrac]], one of [[Senator]] [[Bail Prestor Organa|Bail Organa's]] [[aide]]s, in [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']].

==Biography==
Correa was born in [[Wikipedia:Maringá|Maringá]], [[Wikipedia:Paraná (state)|Paraná]], [[Wikipedia:Brazil|Brazil]].<ref>{{WebCite|url=http://www.fashionmodeldirectory.com/models/caroline_de+souza+correa|text=Caroline De Souza Correa|archivedate=20150105022411}}</ref> She moved to [[Wikipedia:Sydney|Sydney]], [[Wikipedia:Australia|Australia]] at age 20. She occasionally travels back to Brazil to visit. She speaks Brazilian Portuguese and stands 5 feet and 8 inches.

In [[2005]], she appeared in ''Revenge of the Sith''.

